Summary: PuTTY doesn't support the BINARY option
Class: bug
Priority: medium
Difficulty: fun
Present-in: 0.53b 2002-12-29
Content-type: text/x-html-body

<p>
PuTTY doesn't support the TELNET
<a href="ftp://ftp.rfc-editor.org/in-notes/rfc856.txt">BINARY</a> option.
<a href="ftp://ftp.rfc-editor.org/in-notes/rfc1123.txt">RFC 1123</a>
(section 3.3.3)
states that TELNET implementations MUST support it, so its absence is
a bug.
